  "detailed_description": "<h1>Coming soon - Grunn!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Klym is a warm 3D-platformer about climbing buildings and bringing ducklings back to their mother.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1207400/extras/40412df140313fd63a310e3ed7f19018.poster.avif?t=1726497771\" width=420 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1207400/extras/40412df140313fd63a310e3ed7f19018.webm?t=1726497771\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1207400/extras/40412df140313fd63a310e3ed7f19018.mp4?t=1726497771\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10-30 minutes of playtime.<br></li><li> A small warm town to explore.<br></li><li> Grab ledges to climb tall buildings.<br></li><li> 4 cute ducks to find.<br></li><li> Procedural animations.</li></ul><br><strong>Controls</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> WASD keys to move.<br></li><li> Mouse to look around.<br></li><li> Hold & drag the left mouse button to prepare a jump, and then release to set off!<br></li><li> RIght mouse button to let go of ledge.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1207400/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1726497771\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
